item.title: CVE-2023-1783|2023-06-23T21:55:48.800Z -- orangescrum -- orangescrum
item.description: OrangeScrum version 2.0.11 allows an external attacker to remotely obtain AWS instance credentials. This is possible because the application does not properly validate the HTML content to be converted to PDF.
